      <title>土耳其媒体赛前煽动狂热情绪，德国向球迷发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-06/euro-2024-german-police-warns-turkish-fans-ahead-of-class-with-netherlands</link>
